const inputLoginArray = [{
  type: 'email',
  name: 'clientLogin',
  className: 'loginInput',
  classNameSymbol: 'errorSymbol',

  handleButtonClick: true,
  onLogin: false,
  onEnterEmail: false,
  text: 'Войти',
  link: false,
  clientLogin: false,
},
{
  type: 'password',
  name: 'clientPassword',
  className: 'passwordInput',
  classNameSymbol: 'errorSymbolPassword',

  handleButtonClick: false,
  onEnterEmail: true,
  onLogin: true,
  text: 'Забыли пароль?',
  link: false,
  clientLogin: true,
}];

export default inputLoginArray;
